My Cats

Hannah Salomon

February 18, 2018

Description

I have two wonderful cats, which are the loves of my life. They are very dependent compared to most cats, and sometimes they act more like dogs. But I love them just the same.

The names of my cats are:

  • Sunny
  • Karma

They are two different breeds:

Cat Breed
Sunny Maine Coon
Karma Short-haired domestic

Sunny

Sunny is a 7-year-old female. She is a Maine Coon and quite the diva. Her favorite things to do are as follows:

  1. Retrieve toys in exchange for treats
  2. Meow in the middle of the night and wake everyone up
  3. Sleep

Karma

Karma is a 6-year-old male. He is a short-hair domestic cat with slightly special needs. He is the sweetest Mamas boy of a cat. His favorite things to do are as follows:

  1. Get attention
  2. Chase his sister around the house at odd hours of the night
  3. Find warm places to sleep

Do you like cats?

If you or anyone you know are thinking about adopting a cat, there are plenty of reputable adoption agencies in the area:

  • Pennsylvania SPCA
  • ACCT Philly +Animal Care & Control Team of Philadelphia
  • PAWS
  • Philadelphia Animal Welfare Society
